The '''Spain national U-17 basketball team''' ''(Spain Kids national basketball team)'', is the representative for [[Spain]] in international [[basketball]] competitions, and it is organized and run by the [[Spanish Basketball Federation]]. The '''Spain national U-17 basketball team''' represents Spain at the [[FIBA Under-17 World Championship]].
